 {"type": "text", "text": "Refined the active-class test again to use the target `ClassInjector.UsingReflection` path directly.\n\nUpdated file:\n\n`tests/src/org.assertj/assertj-core/3.22.0/src/test/java/org_assertj/assertj_a/ClassInjectorInnerUsingReflectionInnerDispatcherInnerUsingUnsafeOverrideTest.java`\n\nKey change:\n- Replaced `ClassLoadingStrategy.Default.INJECTION` loading with direct use of the public `ClassInjector.UsingReflection` constructor and `injectRaw(...)`.\n- The test now:\n  1. Initializes `ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe` as unavailable through the supported Byte Buddy safe-property path.\n  2. Restores the property.\n  3. Instantiates `ClassInjector.UsingReflection`.\n  4. Injects generated Byte Buddy class bytes through `injectRaw(...)`.\n\nThis should force the `UsingReflection` dispatcher creation path to select `Dispatcher.UsingUnsafeOverride`, reaching its `make(...)`, `initialize(...)`, `findClass(...)`, `getDefinedPackage(...)`, `definePackage(...)`, `getPackage(...)`, and `defineClass(...)` call sites.\n\nI did not run compilation or tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0cc0101d1dece1b4016a25fab2beb48193b64e459e808f5ddb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1420, "output": 1020, "cacheRead": 64512, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 66952, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780873884280, "responseId": "resp_0cc0101d1dece1b4016a25fa9d7b688193be64a9c8dc2c0755"}, "toolResults": []}
